description.excerpt:
Uncertainty estimation in deep learning using deep ensembles with keras
"Simple and Scalable Predictive Uncertainty Estimation using Deep Ensembles"

In this sample, estimate uncertainty in CNN classification of dogs and cats images using deep ensembles. This CNN predict label which indicates dog 1 or cat 0.
Some of the results are shown below.
Fig. The histgram of uncertainty (standart deviation of label).
The details are described in the blog below.

estimate uncertainty in classification of dogs and cats.
Create binary calassification CNN model predcting label and variance.
Treat cifar10 data.
"Simple and Scalable Predictive Uncertainty Estimation using Deep Ensembles"
